TITLE: Episode 30 - The Vixens Meet McAfee
DESCRIPTION: Maddie and Jessie sit down with the one and only John McAfee and discuss politics, running for president under the Libertarian ticket and how to live a meaningful life. This is the zen version of McAfee that most people don’t get to experience.
